Recommends: nginx, certbot
Description: SecuBox APT Repository Manager
 Management interface for the SecuBox APT repository (apt.secubox.in).
 .
 Features:
  - Package management (add, remove, list)
  - GPG key generation and signing
  - Multiple distribution support (bookworm, trixie)
  - Remote sync via rsync
  - Web interface for repository status
 .
 This is the control plane for apt.secubox.in.
